Template:OTRS pending - Wikipedia,"Note to uploaders:
Please copy the URL of this image or article in the email to assist OTRS volunteers to find it. If an email cannot be found in the OTRS system, the content may be deleted for lack of valid licensing information.
"
Template:OTRS pending - Wikipedia,"This template should be used on a file page or article/draft talk page when an email has been sent by the author to the OTRS system.  
"
Template:OTRS pending - Wikipedia,"The file will be added to Category:Items pending OTRS confirmation of permission and if there is a delay in permission being confirmed the file will be progressively categorized under Category:Items pending OTRS confirmation of permission for over 30 days‎, Category:Items pending OTRS confirmation of permission for over 60 days‎, and Category:Items pending OTRS confirmation of permission for over 90 days‎. However, if any edits are made to the file page, the template timer will be reset and the file will be moved back to Category:Items pending OTRS confirmation of permission.
"
Template:OTRS pending - Wikipedia,"The permissions-en backlog is currently 7 days.  If this number is over 10, then the template will transclude this message, ""Please be aware that there is currently a 7-day backlog processing messages sent to the permissions-en queue.""
