"
Wikipedia:Categories for discussion - Wikipedia,"If the listing meets these criteria, simply have the category renamed or merged – follow the instructions at Wikipedia:Categories for discussion/Administrator instructions, in the section ""If the decision is to Rename, Merge, or Delete""; to list it for the bots, use the Speedy moves section.
"
Wikipedia:Categories for discussion - Wikipedia,"
"
Wikipedia:Categories for discussion - Wikipedia,"If the category and desired change do not match one of the criteria mentioned in C2, do not list it here. Instead, list it in the main CFD section.
"
Wikipedia:Categories for discussion - Wikipedia,"If you are in any doubt as to whether it qualifies, do not list it here.
"
Wikipedia:Categories for discussion - Wikipedia,"
Use the following format on a new line at the beginning of the list: "
Wikipedia:Categories for discussion - Wikipedia," (The four ~ will sign and datestamp the entry automatically.)
If the current name should be redirected rather than deleted, use: "
Wikipedia:Categories for discussion - Wikipedia,"Remember to tag the category with: {{subst:Cfr-speedy|New name}}
"
Wikipedia:Categories for discussion - Wikipedia,"A request may be completed if it is more than 48 hours old; that is, if the time stamp shown is earlier than 10:02, 22 December 2020 (UTC). Currently, there are 102 open requests (refresh).
"
Wikipedia:Categories for discussion - Wikipedia,"Check Category:Empty categories awaiting deletion for out of process deletions. In some cases, these will need to be nominated for discussion and the editor who emptied the category informed that they should follow the WP:CFD process.
"
Wikipedia:Categories for discussion - Wikipedia,"Once the renaming has been completed, copy and paste the listing to the Ready for deletion section of Wikipedia:Categories for discussion/Working/Manual.
